flowchart TD
    A([START]) --> B[Validate Input]
    B -->|Valid| C[Analyze Material]
    B -->|Invalid| X[Handle Error]
    C --> D[Generate Summary]
    D --> E[Generate Quiz]
    E --> F[Quality Review]
    F -->|Score < Threshold| G[Revise Output]
    G --> F
    F -->|Score >= Threshold or max revision| H[Finalize]
    X --> I([END])
    H --> I
